Identification - who you are

Authorization - What right you have 

Authentication - proving right, password, smart car

*****Authentication Factors
    Something you know(Password, PIN Code, Captcha)
    Something you have(Smartcard(Chip), driver license, RSA key)
    Something About you(I.E. Biometric, facial recognition)

    Something you do()
    Somewhere you are(i.e. credit card world)